oai_dc:dc.dc:title: RF communication system for professional swimmers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: “Wireless communication system for swimmers” is one of the 27 projects in the European Project Semester 2010. The project has been set by the Danish swimming league Sigma and is to be tackled by a small team of international Students.
